Baik-baik saja maka.

00:10:28.680 --> 00:10:29.880
Anak yang baik!

00:10:30.080 --> 00:10:34.120
Sekarang aku harus pergi.
Hati-hati di jalan.  Baiklah?

00:10:35.160 --> 00:10:38.320
Tapi kamu bisa tinggal
sampai pernikahan ayah, kan?

00:10:42.960 --> 00:10:44.520
Silakan?

00:10:49.760 --> 00:10:51.160
Saya punya ide.

00:10:51.840 --> 00:10:53.800
Bawa ibumu ke sini.

00:11:01.960 --> 00:11:03.400
Benar, ayah?

00:11:10.560 --> 00:11:12.320
Itu ide yang bagus!

00:11:14.560 --> 00:11:16.240
Krishi benar.

